text: Wojciech Szymańczyk (19 February 1943 - 22 November 1996) was a Polish archer. Szymańczyk competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics.Wojciech Szymańczyk ==References== Category:1943 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Polish archers Category:Olympians for Poland Category:Sportspeople from Poznań
